detail.name: Shu
detail.effect:
[Blocker] (After an opponent's attack, you may switch this card to Rest Mode and change the target of the attack to this card.)
[On Play] If you have an energy marker, add up to 1 card with a cost of 3 or less and 《Demon Clan》 in its special traits from your Drop to your hand.
